title: Smart Sweet and Smoky Glazed Beef Meatballs with Apple, Cucumber and Tomato Salad
description: Cranberry spread and chipotle sauce are the secret ingredients in these succulent meatballs. Paired with a crunchy apple, cucumber and tomato salad, it's a simple yet satisfying supper.

